## User Identification Cheat Sheet

```JavaScript
// Identify user with ID and custom attributes
Userback.identify('user_123', {
  email: 'test@example.com',
  plan: 'premium'
});

// Alias a user (if logged in later)
Userback.alias('new_user_id');

// Logout user
Userback.logout();
```

